{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act16d5_level_act16d5_05_beg","storyGroup":"act16d5","storySort":8,"storyDependence":"act16d5_level_act16d5_04_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"WR-5","storyName":"拙山","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"嵯峨向炎熔分享了一段惊心动魄的故事，而当铺的女掌柜黎似乎在想方设法暗示炎熔些线索。克洛丝和乌有也与众人汇合，然而不等各人放心，天色骤变。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act16d5/level_act16d5_05_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act16d5_05","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":6,"next":8,"characters":["炎熔","嵯峨","黎","乌有","克洛丝","墨魉","村民","说书人"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_white","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Character","name":"char_362_Saga#4","id":6},{"type":"PlayMusic","key":"$midautumn","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":9},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":10},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"小僧自幼在东国一座寺庙长大，话虽如此，小僧也只是被住持爷爷收养，并非真正的僧侣。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":11},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"嵯峨这个名，也只是决意下山入世之际，向住持爷爷求来的名字。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":12},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"小僧离开东国后，立志要云游四方。见炎国大好山河，流连忘返，突然忆起年幼时，误闯住持爷爷的阁楼的那一日。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":13},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"那里堆着不少杂物，灰尘蒙蒙，不过有一些少见的玩意，惹得小僧心生童趣。其中，以一大幅绘卷，最是让小僧在意，只记得装那绘卷的箱子，比当时的小僧还高。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":14},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"之后才偶然得知，那是住持爷爷还似小僧如今这般云游时，一路旅途的见证。而那幅绘卷，长近百米，却并非什么名家大作。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":15},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"小僧当时求了住持爷爷半天，才勉为其难地为我摊开了那画卷。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":16},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"时隔多少年了呢，直至今日，小僧仍旧忘不了那日落叶随风而下，当时还健朗的住持爷爷在寺庙大院儿里摊开画卷——小僧，小僧从未见过那般壮丽的山河。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":17},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"更让小僧至今不明的是，那绘卷绝非什么细腻如真，栩栩如生的寻常“名作”，却真能让人一瞬间身临其境，在深秋时节，感受那盛夏飞瀑的勃勃生机——","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":18},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"欸，小僧这“身临其境”，可不是什么形容词。那一瞬间，仿佛真真切切身处画中，如羽兽掠林而去。山峦叠起，卵石盈池，树影婆娑，飞瀑直下，恢弘可闻！","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":19},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"不过恍惚间回过神来，小僧又似乎只是被画卷吸引，痴痴望着那绘卷罢了。印象里，小僧甚至还打了些个寒颤，从盛夏山川回到那深秋小院的印象，就更加深刻了。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":20},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"住持爷爷告诉小僧，这幅画，是因他在大炎苦潭江上的一场偶遇而来。当时的住持爷爷比小僧如今还要年轻些许，只是个小沙弥，正逢节度使南巡，官道不通，只好泛舟渡江。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":21},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"行到江中，千帆竞发，却能远远眺望到一叶孤舟，沿江而下，仿佛不属于这生机勃勃的景象。住持爷爷一时好奇，就跟了上去。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":22},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"那叶孤舟不紧不慢，不急不缓。住持爷爷只隔船见了她一眼，好似登天岳前望天顶，云缭雾绕。一时间竟是惊慌失措，险些落水，一呼一吸间，却又被那人救起。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":23},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"那位女子风华绝代，一言不发，带着住持爷爷一路沿江而下，直到吠山渡下船，往灰齐山方向走。住持爷爷为报答救命之恩，一路为她生柴做饭，背行囊，砍荆棘，披星戴月。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":24},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"女子似乎从不需要睡眠，而住持爷爷每晚睡去，都会梦见一段从未见过的往事。醒来之后，却又沉沉忘记，若有若无。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":25},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"如此反复数次，住持爷爷也陷入了长久的思考，两个明明并肩而行的旅人，却像各行陌路一般，深陷在自己的孤独中反思自己。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":26},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"直到某天，二人来到一处山川秀丽之地，女子有感而发，驻足眺望，一望就是几个时辰。住持爷爷问她在做什么，她说，在画。在画一幅拙山尽起图。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":27},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"住持爷爷忍不住打了个盹，等到赫然惊醒，却发现自己仍在苦潭江上的扁舟之内。根本没有什么吠山渡，也没有那位山上神仙似的女子。唯独眼前多出了一幅绘卷，便是这幅画。","x":"200","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.1","width":"900","id":28},{"type":"Subtitle","id":29},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":30},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":31},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":32},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_pawnshop","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"1","id":33},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":34},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.4","id":35,"musicid":1},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......那位女性叫什么？","id":37,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_362_Saga#4","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"不知。","id":39,"figure":"char_362_Saga#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"没问过？","id":41,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_362_Saga#4","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"也不敢呐。","id":43,"figure":"char_362_Saga#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......","id":45,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_362_Saga","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"再说那如梦似幻，如真似假，兴许是一年半载，又或是弹指一瞬，恍神之间，这上哪儿问去？","id":47,"figure":"char_362_Saga"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1","id":48},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......","id":49,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_362_Saga","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"小僧游历炎国，有意无意回想起这个故事，细细想来，兴许只是住持爷爷敷衍我而胡乱编的故事罢了。","id":51,"figure":"char_362_Saga"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"不过小僧在炎国四处打听，这幅《拙山尽起图》竟然还小有名气。","id":52,"figure":"char_362_Saga"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"相传是一位约百年前的无名画家所留，曾有皇亲国戚重金求而不得，因此闻名。","id":53,"figure":"char_362_Saga"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"正巧到了灰齐山附近，小僧便突发奇想，想借机去看看是否能找到那画中的奇景......","id":54,"figure":"char_362_Saga"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"哈哈，在山中寻到一处山清水秀之地，反应过来时，就已经身在此处啦。","id":55,"figure":"char_362_Saga"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"灰齐山上的那栋茅屋，这倒是和我们如出一辙......","id":57,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......这里会是一场梦吗？","id":58,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_362_Saga","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"如是一场大梦，那对施主来说，小僧便是梦中幻象，那小僧说的话，也就不可信了。","id":60,"figure":"char_362_Saga"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"若是不可信了，炎熔施主又如何判断眼前的景色，是梦非梦？","id":61,"figure":"char_362_Saga"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"慢点......你要把我绕晕了......","id":63,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"那你知道怎么离开这里吗？","id":64,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_362_Saga","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"小僧云游至今，仍未明白如何主动离开此地。","id":66,"figure":"char_362_Saga"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......至今？你在这里呆了多久？","id":68,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_362_Saga#4","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"很久很久啦，细细数来......","id":70,"figure":"char_362_Saga#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":71},{"type":"Character","id":72},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":73},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#5","fadetime":"0.5","id":74},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"二位的茶就要凉了，别光顾着说话，品一品茶吧。","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_139#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"啊......谢谢。","id":78,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"（呼......）","id":79,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#5","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1","focus":"2","id":80},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......嗯？说起来，黎小姐，难道也是......？","id":81,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1","focus":"1","id":82},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"只是本地的当铺掌柜罢了。","id":83,"figure":"avg_npc_139#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#4","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1","focus":"1","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"炎熔小姐......我很欣赏你的善良，也很钦佩你从墨魉手下保护镇民的意愿，但有时候，请多考虑一下自己的安危。","id":85,"figure":"avg_npc_139#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#4","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1","focus":"2","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"那些怪物对罗德岛的精锐构不成威胁。","id":87,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_362_Saga","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"此话不假，炎熔施主一身好本领，无需担心！","id":89,"figure":"char_362_Saga"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#5","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1","focus":"1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"......若真是如此，也好。","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_139#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"炎熔小姐，我有一个问题，不知当不当问。","id":92,"figure":"avg_npc_139#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#5","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1","focus":"2","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"问吧，其实不用对我们这么拘谨的......","id":94,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#2","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1","focus":"1","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"炎熔小姐，你可端详过水中的月亮？","id":96,"figure":"avg_npc_139#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"无论水中月色会被粼粼波光扯碎成什么模样，待到风平浪静时，它还会是那轮圆月。","id":97,"figure":"avg_npc_139#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"若是因为怜悯那一时闪烁的水中月色，因此湿了鞋，着了凉，是大没有必要的。","id":98,"figure":"avg_npc_139#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"炎熔小姐，你可会为了捞那一轮水中月......费尽心思？","id":99,"figure":"avg_npc_139#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#5","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","focus":"2","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"不......应该不会？做这种事儿没什么意义吧？","id":101,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"怎么突然说这个？","id":102,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#5","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","focus":"1","id":103},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"......我不知炎熔小姐的那轮明月是何模样，也就无法提醒炎熔小姐到底差在何处。不过水中月，终归是水中月罢了。","id":104,"figure":"avg_npc_139#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"没必要为了我们，做到这个份上。","id":105,"figure":"avg_npc_139#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#5","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","focus":"2","id":106},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你是说......？","id":107,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":108},{"type":"Character","id":109},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":110},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":111},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":112},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.7","id":113},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","fadetime":"1","id":114},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":115},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"恩人！恩人！你没事吧？","id":117,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"......啊呀，连茶都泡上了，居然不喊我。","id":119,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#4","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"这二位想必也是婆山镇的贵客吧？我去泡茶，顺路拿些糕点，你们慢叙。","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_139#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":122},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":123},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":124},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":125},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":126},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"那位是？","id":128,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"是这里的掌柜，名字叫黎，黎明的黎。","id":130,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":131},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"恩人，那些墨魉呢？哦哦，我知道了！一定是恩人神威无敌，把它们全都赶跑啦！","id":132,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"——那个小女孩安全了吗？","id":134,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"她安全了，没事的。","id":136,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":137},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"呜呜呜，恩人呐，你怎么如此不信任我......我趟过刀山火海也未流泪的，现在倒是有几分心酸......！","id":138,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Dialog","id":139},{"type":"Character","id":140},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":141},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":142},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":143},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#4","fadetime":"1","id":144},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"二位，茶水。","id":146,"figure":"avg_npc_139#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"嗯嗯......闻着就感觉到是很昂贵的茶叶呢。","id":148,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"恩人好见识！像我这种凡夫俗子，只觉得苦，完全尝不出滋味哩。","id":150,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#5","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"只是寻常茶叶罢了。镇上集市，只有卖这一种茶叶，若是不合意，还请见谅。","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_139#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"呼啊~虽然习惯了红茶和咖啡，但是偶尔品一品大炎的茶叶，也别有一番滋味嘛。","id":154,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_362_Saga#1","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","text":"小僧家乡也有堪称别具滋味的茶叶，若是有机会，请务必让小僧小露一手。","id":156,"figure":"char_362_Saga#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"呼啊......","id":158,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"哎呀，小炎熔，你犯困了？","id":160,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"没有。只是突然放松下来罢了......","id":162,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":163},{"type":"Character","id":164},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":165},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_139#5","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黎","text":"茶水养心，几位劳烦的事情，不是靠奔波劳累就能解决的。","id":167,"figure":"avg_npc_139#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_362_Saga#1","focus":"1","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......还是没什么线索啊。","id":169,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_362_Saga#1","focus":"2","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"嵯峨","te